OL,6,FOrganisers of a major Pride event have
OL,7,Fcut ties with the Conservative Party's
OL,8,Fbiggest donor following a row over
OL,9,Falleged racist comments about MP Diane
OL,10,FAbbott.
OL,12,FLeeds Pride said it was "imperative"
OL,13,Fto reassess its sponsorship deal with
OL,14,F's company TPP.
OL,16,FIn a statement, it said the decision
OL,17,Fwas a "stand against discrimination".
