OL,6,FThe move follows controversy over
OL,7,Fcomments reportedly made by Mr Hester,
OL,8,Fwho has donated more than #10million
OL,9,Fto the Tories, at his firm's Leeds
OL,10,Fheadquarters.
OL,12,FIn remarks first reported by The
OL,13,FGuardian, Mr Hester allegedly said Ms
OL,14,FAbbott made him "want to hate all
OL,15,Fblack women" and "should be shot".
OL,17,FHe later apologised for making "rude"
OL,18,Fremarks but said they "had nothing to
OL,19,Fdo with her gender nor colour of skin".
